import base64 def out(file): f = open(file, &#34;rb&#34;).read() print(file + &#34;:&#34; + &#34;\n&#34; + &#34;16进制格式为：&#34;) print(f.hex() + &#34;\n&#34;) f_b64 = base64.b64encode(f) print(&#34;base64格式为：&#34;) print(str(f_b64) + &#34;\n&#34;) if __name__ == &#39;__main__&#39;: out(&#34;poc.bin&#34;) Java
import java.io.IOException; import java.nio.file.Files; import java.nio.file.Paths; import java.util.Base64; public class FileConversion { public static void main(String[] args) { String filePath = &#34;ser.txt&#34;; try { byte[] fileBytes = Files.readAllBytes(Paths.get(filePath)); String hexString = bytesToHex(fileBytes); System.out.println(filePath + &#34;:\n16进制格式为：\n&#34; + hexString); String base64String = Base64.getEncoder().encodeToString(fileBytes); System.out.println(&#34;Base64格式为：\n&#34; + base64String); } catch (IOException e) { e.printStackTrace(); } } private static String bytesToHex(byte[] bytes) { StringBuilder hexString = new StringBuilder(); for (byte b : bytes) { hexString.append(String.format(&#34;%02x&#34;, b)); } return hexString.toString(); } }
